e.org/web/20141126051441/http://sgiff.com/films/men-who-save-the-world/|archivedate=26 November 2014}}</ref>\n|Asian Feature Film\n|Sharon Gan \n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|3rd Nara International Film Festival <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mediahiburan.karangkraf.com/terkini/lelaki-harapan-dunia-ke-2-festival-filem-antarabangsa-1.315671 |title=Archived copy |access-date=15 November 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141123024714/http://mediahiburan.karangkraf.com/terkini/lelaki-harapan-dunia-ke-2-festival-filem-antarabangsa-1.315671 |archive-date=23 November 2014 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.murai.com.my/berita/tempatan/article/articleid/611347/lelaki-harapan-dunia-tayang-di-2-festival-filem-antarabangsa-bulan-ini|title=Lelaki Harapan Dunia Tayang Di 2 Festival Filem Antarabangsa Bulan Ini|publisher=}}</ref>\n|Main Competition\n|Sharon Gan\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Golden Horse Film Festival and Awards|Golden Horse Film Festival and Awards 2014]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dailyseni.com/index.php/home/news/film-tv/item/1946-lelaki-harapan-dunia-terpilih-ke-festival-filem-taipei-golden-horse|title=Lelaki Harapan Dunia Terpilih ke Festival Filem Taipei Golden Horse|author=The Daily Seni|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://terbakor.com/2014/11/14/lelaki-harapan-dunia-terpilih-ke-festival-filem-golden-horse-taipei/|title=Lelaki Harapan Dunia terpilih ke Festival Filem Golden Horse, Taipei|work=Terbakor !}}</ref>\n|Asian Window\n|Sharon Gan \n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[Kolkata International Film Festival]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.budiey.com/lelaki-harapan-dunia-terpilih-ke-festival-filem-antarabangsa-kolkata/|title=Lelaki Harapan Dunia Terpilih Ke Festival Filem Antarabangsa Kolkata|work=Sensasi Selebriti}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tupai.com.my/2014/11/lelaki-harapan-dunia-terpilih-ke.html|title=\"Lelaki Harapan Dunia\" terpilih ke Festival Filem Kolkata|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129022525/http://www.tupai.com.my/2014/11/lelaki-harapan-dunia-terpilih-ke.html|archivedate=29 November 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wom.my/berita-terkini/lelaki-harapan-dunia/|title=Lelaki Harapan Dunia \u2013 Women Online Magazine|work=Women Online Magazine}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://my.entertainment.yahoo.com/news/lelaki-harapan-dunia-terpilih-ke-festival-filem-kolkata-035300944.html|title=\"Lelaki Harapan Dunia\" terpilih ke Festival Filem Kolkata|date=7 November 2014|work=Yahoo}}</ref>\n|Asian Select (NETPAC Award)\n|Sharon Gan\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[International Film Festival Rotterdam|2015 International Film Festival Rotterdam]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.iffr.com/en/films/lelaki-harapan-dunia/|title=Men Who Save the World \u2013 IFFR.COM \u2013 International Film Festival Rotterdam 2015 \u2013 IFFR|work=iffr.com|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150115080751/https://www.iffr.com/en/films/lelaki-harapan-dunia/|archivedate=15 January 2015}}</ref>\n|Bright Future\n|Sharon Gan\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[G\u00f6teborg International Film Festival|2015 G\u00f6teborg International Film Festival]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://filmweb01.filmfestival.org/filmfestival/info/en/festivalprogram/programentry?filmId=186911|title=G\u00f6teborg Film Festival|website=filmweb01.filmfestival.org|accessdate=10 May 2017}}</ref>\n|Den gudomliga komedin\n|Sharon Gan\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"13\"| 27th Malaysian Film Festival (FFM) <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cinema.com.my/bm/articles/news_details.aspx?search=2015.n_lelakiharapandunia13nominationsbm_24855&title=-Lelaki-Harapan-Dunia-dapat-13-pencalonan-di-FFM27|title=cinema.com.my: \"Lelaki Harapan Dunia\" dapat 13 pencalonan di FFM27|work=cinema.com.my}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.astroawani.com/entertainment-news/mff27-journey-wins-4-trophies-including-best-director-and-best-actor-72344|title=MFF27: The Journey wins 4 trophies, including Best Director and Best Actor|work=astroawani.com}}</ref>\n| Best Picture\n| Everythings Film Sdn Bhd\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Director\n| Liew Seng Tat\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Actor\n| Wan Hanafi Su\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Screenplay\n| Liew Seng Tat\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Story\n| Liew Seng Tat\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Cinematography\n| Teoh Gay Hian\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Editing\n| Liew Seng Tat\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Sound Editing\n| Imaginax Studios \n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Art Editing\n| Tunku Mohd Taufek \n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Original Score\n| Imaginax Studios\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Costume Design\n| Tunku Mohd Taufek\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| Best Child Actor\n| Raykarl Iskandar\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Muhammad Farhan\n| {{nom}} \n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\"|  Kuala Lumpur Film Critics Society Awards 2015 <ref>{{cite web|url=http://tontonfilem.blogspot.my/2015/09/senarai-pencalonan-anugerah-majlis.html|title=TONTONFILEM|work=blogspot.my}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ampfkl.blogspot.my/2015/10/keputusan-anugerah-majlis-pengkritik.html |title=Men Who Save the World}}</ref> \n| Best Picture\n| Everythings Film Sdn Bhd\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Director\n| Liew Seng Tat\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Actor\n| Wan Hanafi Su\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Screenplay\n| Liew Seng Tat\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Cinematography\n| Teoh Gay Hian\n| {{won}}\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of submissions to the 88th Academy Awards for Best Foreign Language Film]]\n* [[List of Malaysian submissions for the Academy Award for Best Foreign Language Film]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb title|3797880|Men Who Save the World}}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20160504073300/http://lhd.everythingfilms.net/en/ Official website]\n* [https://www.facebook.com/lelakiharapandunia Official Facebook page]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Men Who Save The World}}\n[[Category:2014 films]]\n[[Category:2010s comedy films]]\n[[Category:Malaysian films]]\n[[Category:Malaysian comedy films]]\n[[Category:Dutch films]]\n[[Category:Dutch comedy films]]\n[[Category:German films]]\n[[